	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Stuck with fixed width font, it is very easy to write text on the NES' screen.
<br />Load each letter in pattern table and write the corresponding tile number on name tables.
<br />If you arrange the letters in pattern table in maneer they matches ASCI definition, you just have to copy the text data to the nametable and go to the next row when a return character is encountered.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


